text: Goe gaa made i di aumaalia, gei di madagoaa ma ga danu iei goe, nia daangada gaa dudu nadau ‘incense’ adu gi di goe, gadoo be di nadau hai dela ne dudu nadau tigidaumaha kala i di danu o damana mmaadua ala nogo king i oo mua. Digaula ga tangitangi gi di goe mo di hai boloo, ‘Di madau king guu made!’ Au go Dimaadua ne helekai.”
